{"tid":1595593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"與李小加出席同一論壇 倫交所CEO：上海才是中國金融中心","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T07:10:40.000Z","uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"80741330c439f8f019f9fa4e116047ba6b839a24","tid":1595593,"uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"偉大的上海應該要做全球金融市場~做中國金融中心太短淺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n倫交所行政總裁David Schwimmer與港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=13613dd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)行政總裁李小加日前出席倫敦的SIBOS論壇，外電報道，Schwimmer在論壇上表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然香港在全球金融市場定位強勁，惟長遠而言，上海才是中國的金融中心。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n李小加在倫敦同一論壇表示，由於中國銀行體系當中有27萬億美元的資金需作出配置，目前是創立一個全球交易所的時機。<br />\n<br />\n李小加和Schwimmer均表示，中國不會急於放寬資本管制，惟Schwimmer稱這是無可避免的事情，李小加認為中國放寬資本管制需時20年或以上時間達成。(ka/t)~<br />\n<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=985dec0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"4333b9e186a795b188f435a5f1918804474507c5","tid":1595593,"uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"923d340a790258700cbe0a6544916f3fb033ba5d","tid":1595593,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:39:11.000Z","msg":"鳩up一句野要比乜代價？"},{"pid":"cecd95a7cfa78a82117348c1dd0f478bf234f27c","tid":1595593,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"上海人識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f7a3e6d64605bd7266f67dc509be04f972cb12","tid":1595593,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2